 all the aspects related to the impairment assessment considered by OMPL and the outcome thereon, it has been assessed that no impairment of assets of the subsidiary Company OMPL would arise during the period under consideration and accordingly no impairment of OMPL's assets has been considered in the Consolidated Financial Statements of the Group for the quarter and nine months ended 31.12.2021.'    8 Consolidated Segment wise Revenue Results Assets and liabilities (Refer table in full format).   9 Additional Disclosures as per SEBI (listing Obligation and Disclosure Requirements) Regulations, 2015 (Table).   10 Previous period figures have been regrouped/reclassified, wherever necessary.</in-bse-fin:DisclosureOfNotesOnFinancialResultsExplanatoryTextBlock>
